message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for $100. I believe it offers great value at this price.
Hello Alice, I appreciate your offer, but I believe I can find a better deal elsewhere. I am willing to pay $90 for the product.
Hi Bob, I understand your position, but I'm confident in the value of this product. How about we meet in the middle at $95?
Hello Alice, I appreciate your willingness to negotiate, but I still think $90 would be a fair price for the product. I hope we can come to an agreement.
